snippet.title: Air/Sea Battle - VC 4000
snippet.description: The three main modes of this cassette. Ship vs submarines, Plane vs rocket launcher and Missile launcher vs "Everything". This game is a lot of fun. Great graphics and action, but few missiles in each game. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/02/airsea-battle-7-vc-4000.html
